    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Species of cedar native to the Atlas Mountains of Algeria and Morocco. Some classifications list it as a subspecies of Lebanon Cedar, as C. libani atlantica.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
